  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      It has been shown in laboratory studies that pomegranate juice contains anti-viral action
      against influenza. The researchers wish to investigate the effect of pomegranate juice on
      patients suffering from influenza A (seasonal or swine flu).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
